## **_ITS TIME FOR SATURDAY NIGHT'S MAIN EVENT_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/92fed2c2-4b24-43b8-8920-eb170cbfd7a6/22193.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE Championship: Cody Rhodes def. Drew McIntyre_**
    

Drew McIntyre tries to hit Cody Rhodes with the title when the ref was down but missed.

Both men were down and then Cody Rhodes deliberately cheated by checking if the ref was down before DDT'ing Drew McIntyre onto the WWE Championship and then hitting a CrossRhodes for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f7ac9f3d-63a3-47a9-9bf9-7712958446b4/22194.jpg)

Nick Aldis checks in with Tiffany Stratton to make sure she's in a good state of mind to face Jade Cargill tonight. Stratton says she's ready.  

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d709fa7f-62a0-428b-84e7-f988468b6d00/22202.jpg)

*   ## **_Jade Cargill essentially SQUASHED Tiffany Stratton to win the WWE Women's Championship!!!_**
    

Jade beats Tiffany Stratton down pretty soundly. Taking 90% of the match for her own offense, leaving Tiffany on the defensive until she fell to a powerbomb and then a Jaded.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/65e14131-f89d-47e6-be73-4ea358917a6a/22210.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE Intercontinental Championship: Dominik Mysterio def Rusev and Penta_**
    

Rusev had Penta in the Accolade, the bell rung and he thought he won the title. But it was Dom Mysterio ringing the bell to break up the submission.

Dom brings the bell hammer into the ring, Penta takes it from Dom, swings it at Dom, hits Rusev instead.

Dom throws Penta out of the ring, and hits a Frog Splash on Rusev to retain.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d5001f9a-c5d2-4c3e-a6fc-3ed90550912d/22214.jpg)

## **_🚨_**[**_BREAKING🚨 16 Man Tournament Announced to Decide John Cena's Final Opponent_**](https://comicbookclique.com/wrestling-news/john-cena-final-match-tournament-announced)

John Cena announced his final opponent will be decided with this tournament that will involve wrestlers from WWE "and who don't even work here"

It will begin on November 10th RAW in Boston

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/950d9577-18d0-4419-8f1f-5639f3d10117/22221.jpg)

*   ## **_World Heavyweight Championship: CM Punk defeats Jey Uso_**
    

CM Punk is the WWE World Heavyweight Champion!!!!

